  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package declares signatureAlg ed25519 and provides a hash but omits the actual signature value, representing a partially-signed artifact that cannot be verified for structural integrity (W-SI-01).",
